      "title": "ULTRASOUND SHORT SCAN | Quick, Safe & Same-Day Results | Cadabams Diagnostics",
      "description": "Discover how a ULTRASOUND SHORT SCAN at Cadabams Diagnostics gives expectant parents fast reassurance in just 5–10 minutes. Learn preparation, benefits, and pricing.",
